title: #92Noon! 10a Hour 4/21 - Reid/Smith
description: Wild radio analyst Tom Reid stops by to reminisce about the old days of hockey & discuss rivalries in the NHL.  Plus, new Vikings linebacker Za'Darius Smith joins the show to talk about bouncing back from a back injury, building team camaraderie, & more!
